1. *Salatu* volim da jedem sa pilećim mesom. (I like to eat *salad* with chicken.)
2. *Salatu* sam napravila od paradajza, krastavaca i feta sira. (I made *salad* from tomatoes, cucumbers, and feta cheese.)
3. Da li želite da vam *salatu* poslužim kao predjelo ili kao prilog? (Would you like me to serve you *salad* as an appetizer or as a side dish?)
4. Sinoć smo jeli testeninu sa *salatom* od rukole. (Last night we had pasta with *arugula salad*.)
5. Molim vas da mi donesete još malo *salate*. (Please bring me some more *salad*.)

(Note: In Serbian, the word "salata" can refer to any type of salad, including vegetable salads, fruit salads, pasta salads, etc.)